high_descs: Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the sink.
Pick up wine bottle from the sink.
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the counter top on your right.
Place wine bottle on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Changing wine bottle from one place to another.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the sink.
Pick the wine bottle from it.
Turn left and walk back towards the countertop
Place the wine bottle on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: To Place the wine bottle on the counter top.

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the sink
Pick up wine bottle from the sink
Turn around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the countertop
